Some thing to say...
There have been constant problems since the 6.0.0 version update, and the main reason is that the upgrade was too hasty and led to some mistakes in decision-making. After this period of repairs, it should be back to road. Thank you for continuing to use and report problems. Due to some personal affairs that need to be dealt with later, the later plan is to deal with issues in every two weeks. Please understand 🙏.

You can use this extension to convert the ugoira on Pixiv to animation like gif or video like mp4, or download the images of manga or save novel as file.
You can also download images from Pixiv Comic and Pixiv Fanbox (Notice: You need to have access to the post or comic you want to download in order to download the resource).

You can feel free to open issue on GitHub if you have any questions.

Github:
Pixiv Toolkit: https://github.com/leoding86/webextension-pixiv-toolkit
